Insertion Sort to Sort allItems Array in ascending price 

LOOP through Array starting at element [1]
    SET value to Item.price loop is On
    SET current to Item at index loop in on

    SET toCompare to index loop is on

        WHILE toCompare > 0 && Array[toCompare - 1].getPrice > value
           SET Array[toCompare] to Array[toCompare - 1]
           SET toCompare to toCompare - 1
        END While
    Array[toCompare] = current
END LOOP










